Job Description
Are you looking to work in a dynamic environment where YOU can make a difference?
Novartis is looking for ambitious and energetic candidates (male/female) who are effective team players with leadership qualities to join us as part of our Sales Team in the capacity of "Medical Information Officers" to be based at following locations:
- Karachi
- Hyderabad
- Sukkur
- Multan
- Lahore/Gujranwala
- Faisalabad/Sargodha
- Rawalpindi/Islamabad
- Peshawar
Candidate must meet following criteria:
Science Graduates (preferably Pharmacy) 1-2 years sales experience in Pharmaceuticals, sound knowledge of geographical areas, good communication skills, computer literate.Company OverviewNovartis is a research based global leader in healthcare, with more than 135,000 associates around the globe with affiliates in more than 140 countries. We share a vision of a better today and tomorrow for patients - a vision that drives our growth and success.
Our purpose is to care and to cure and part of this purpose is working to enhance access to our medicines. More than 1.2 billion patients around the world are treated by Novartis products annually.Apply Instructions for This Job
